dct_description_sm: Map shows roads, mangroves, wadi, populated areas, airfield, nomad camps, and landmarks of note. Includes location map, boundaries diagram, glossary, and guide to numbered features. "Compiled in 1983 from best available sources." "Printed by DMAHTC 9-84."
